description:
Britain and Ireland's Next Top Model - Cycle 9, Episode 2




The contestants head to the National Wedding Show at Birmingham's NEC to be coached in the art of the catwalk by model Jade Parfitt, and take part in a magazine cover shoot directed by Dannii Minogue, who is looking for a girl with star quality to make copies fly off the shelves.



Original Air Date: 20-Jun-2013
